data.title: Why wasn't White Fang reanimated?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 2): It wasn't mentioned anywhere. Kabuto never talked about Sakumo (the White Fang)when showing off or discussing his reanimations.

We can only assume:

 * They never found a body, or it was so well guarded that Kabuto couldn't get a DNA sample.
